{"tid":318043,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE狀元出爐　來自女拔聖保羅男女等傳統名校","createTime":"2017-07-12T00:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T15:14:38.000Z","uid":51978,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86bc53a701481e73e8719fbdb09007a7ba1d3c7e","tid":318043,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:18:40.000Z","msg":"今屆一名超級狀元來自傳統名校拔萃女書院。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試DSE今日(12日)放榜，今年誕生6名考獲7科5**的狀元，分別是3男3女，當中包括1名考獲7科5**兼修讀數學延伸部分同樣考獲5**的超級女狀元。據了解，狀元來自傳統名校拔萃女書院、庇理羅士女子中學、聖保羅男女中學、皇仁書院及九龍民生書院。<br />\n<br />\n拔萃女書院今年誕生1名女狀元；聖保羅男女中學誕生2名狀元，包括1男1女；庇理羅士女子中學誕生1名女狀元；皇仁書院誕生1名男狀元；九龍民生書院誕生1名男狀元。"},{"pid":"e5f6277f683584538eb0ae67fe0c71ad3fb82125","tid":318043,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實啲記者點收風知道邊間學校出咗狀元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學校自己通知傳媒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無行內人或知情人士解下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8f809e60dd6fa8657f03d4bce6598e4715afc5","tid":318043,"uid":24752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06159716a1cab65a456ff471fba4f81b1f2fddc2","tid":318043,"uid":120499,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"St. Paul Co-Ed 真係好屈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fe6a6eae8c333765f091866a9f0f9fae85ad0b","tid":318043,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>St. Paul Co-Ed 真係好屈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>但係皇仁歷屆文憑試狀元總數多過佢"},{"pid":"78988bbf7b53dbfa968d39b314454e835f656713","tid":318043,"uid":51978,"li